{"timestamp": "2025-12-02 14:24:54.753263", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Done — I submitted the solution.\n\nSummary of what I submitted\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"pc_0_1\", \"leaf_router_0_1\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"host_missing_ip\", \"southbound_port_mismatch\"]\n\nReasoning (brief)\n- pc_0_1 has no eth0/IP configured (only loopback present) → host_missing_ip.\n- leaf_router_0_1 has the 10.0.1.0/24 host subnet bound to eth4 while the topology shows the host should be on eth2 → southbound_port_mismatch.\n\nIf you want, I can now:\n- Provide exact remediation steps to fix the host and router interface assignments, or\n- Run additional targeted diagnostics (pc_0_1 ip link/dmesg, tcpdump on leaf_router_0_1 eth2/eth4) before remediation. Which would you prefer?", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2470, "output_tokens": 195, "total_tokens": 2665, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
